# Fluff Date: 2026-03-18 15:07:44
<overview>
<p>Drawing veterans from the Com Guards, recruits from the Free Worlds League, and volunteers from Protectorate worlds, the Word of Blake Militia assembled infantry formations whose quality varied but whose equipment was consistently first-rate. Manning assault-class field autocannon, these gun crews bring devastating close-range firepower that can cripple armored vehicles and even threaten BattleMech limbs, though the weapon's bulk limits mobility and rate of repositioning.</p>
</overview>

